snippet.textDisplay:
Zindagi jab mushkil huvi lockdown me. Toh aur taqleef aayi aur jab aayi taqleef toh soch kar darne laga ki ab zinda bhi kaise rahu tab meri Godh me ek Nannhi si Jaan dedi. Khuda ne Taqleefein toh di hi hai lekin ab unse ladne ki Wajah bhi. Aisi Himmath mili sirf chand lamhon ki us nanhi si jaan ko Zindagi se Ladte dekha. Tab pata chala ki Khuda ki ye zindagi kitni Taqat rakhti hai aur judi kitna hai Khuda se. Shukr hai Zayd ke liye Allah. Shukr hai Zayd ka.
- Father.
